<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Genshin Companion — ตัวช่วยเล่น Genshin Impact</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Thai:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Cinzel:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #080C18;
      --bg-nav: rgba(8,12,24,0.92);
      --card: rgba(255,255,255,0.055);
      --card-hover: rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      --border-gold: rgba(201,168,76,0.40);
      --gold: #C9A84C;
      --gold-light: #E8CC7C;
      --text: #EDE8D8;
      --text-2: #9DA8BE;
      --text-3: #5A6480;
      --success: #4CAF50;
      --warning: #FF9800;
      --radius: 12px;
      /* Elements */
      --pyro: #FF6B35;   --pyro-bg: rgba(255,107,53,0.12);
      --hydro: #4FC3F7;  --hydro-bg: rgba(79,195,247,0.12);
      --anemo: #4DB6AC;  --anemo-bg: rgba(77,182,172,0.12);
      --electro: #CE93D8;--electro-bg: rgba(206,147,216,0.12);
      --cryo: #80DEEA;   --cryo-bg: rgba(128,222,234,0.12);
      --geo: #FFD54F;    --geo-bg: rgba(255,213,79,0.12);
      --dendro: #A5D6A7; --dendro-bg: rgba(165,214,167,0.12);
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', system-ui, sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ---- STARS ---- */
    #stars {
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .star {
      position: absolute;
      background: #fff; border-radius: 50%;
      animation: twinkle var(--dur, 3s) ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes twinkle {
      0%,100% { opacity: var(--lo,.1); }
      50%      { opacity: var(--hi,.8); }
    }

    /* ---- LAYOUT ---- */
    .app { position: relative; z-index: 1; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

    /* ---- HEADER ---- */
    header {
      background: var(--bg-nav);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      padding: 0 16px;
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    }
    .header-inner {
      max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 0 0; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .logo {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .logo small {
      display: block; font-size: 10px; font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-3); font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0; margin-top: 1px;
    }

    /* ---- TABS ---- */
    .tabs { display: flex; gap: 2px; overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; }
    .tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
    .tab {
      padding: 10px 15px 12px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-2); background: none; border: none;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; cursor: pointer;
      white-space: nowrap; font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif;
      transition: color .18s, border-color .18s;
    }
    .tab:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .tab.active { color: var(--gold); border-bottom-color: var(--gold); }

    /* ---- MAIN ---- */
    main {
      flex: 1; max-width: 960px; width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 16px 60px;
    }
    .section { display: none; }
    .section.active { display: block; }

    /* ---- CARDS ---- */
    .card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    .card-gold { border-color: var(--border-gold); }
    .card-title {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-3);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .card-title .accent { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ---- ELEMENT BADGES ---- */
    .el {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 3px;
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    .el-Pyro    { background: var(--pyro-bg);    color: var(--pyro);    border-color: rgba(255,107,53,.25); }
    .el-Hydro   { background: var(--hydro-bg);   color: var(--hydro);   border-color: rgba(79,195,247,.25); }
    .el-Anemo   { background: var(--anemo-bg);   color: var(--anemo);   border-color: rgba(77,182,172,.25); }
    .el-Electro { background: var(--electro-bg); color: var(--electro); border-color: rgba(206,147,216,.25); }
    .el-Cryo    { background: var(--cryo-bg);    color: var(--cryo);    border-color: rgba(128,222,234,.25); }
    .el-Geo     { background: var(--geo-bg);     color: var(--geo);     border-color: rgba(255,213,79,.25); }
    .el-Dendro  { background: var(--dendro-bg);  color: var(--dendro);  border-color: rgba(165,214,167,.25); }

    /* ---- RESIN ---- */
    .resin-num {
      font-size: 52px; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      color: var(--gold); line-height: 1;
    }
    .resin-bar-bg {
      height: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 999px; margin: 10px 0; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .resin-bar-fill {
      height: 8px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), #a78bfa);
      transition: width .4s ease;
    }
    input[type=range] {
      width: 100%; accent-color: var(--gold);
      margin-top: 6px; cursor: pointer;
    }

    /* ---- TASKS ---- */
    .task {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none; transition: opacity .2s;
    }
    .task:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .task.done { opacity: 0.4; }
    .task.done .task-label { text-decoration: line-through; }
    .task input[type=checkbox] { width: 17px; height: 17px; accent-color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; cursor: pointer; }
    .task-badge { margin-left: auto; font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px; white-space: nowrap; }
    .tb-gold    { background: rgba(201,168,76,.15); color: var(--gold); }
    .tb-warning { background: rgba(255,152,0,.15);  color: var(--warning); }

    /* ---- DOMAIN ---- */
    .domain-row {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
      padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px;
    }
    .domain-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .domain-icon { font-size: 18px; width: 28px; text-align: center; flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 1px; }
    .domain-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 2px; font-size: 13px; }
    .domain-items { color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.5; font-size: 12px; }

    /* ---- WISH ---- */
    .wish-row {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 13px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .wish-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .wish-name { flex: 1; min-width: 120px; color: var(--text-2); }
    .wish-pity { font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold-light); min-width: 56px; font-size: 13px; }
    .wish-input {
      width: 120px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 5px 10px; color: var(--text); font-size: 12px;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif; outline: none;
      transition: border-color .2s;
    }
    .wish-input:focus { border-color: var(--border-gold); }

    /* ---- FILTER ROW ---- */
    .filter-row { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .filter-btn {
      font-size: 12px; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border); background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      color: var(--text-2); cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif; transition: all .18s;
    }
    .filter-btn:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); color: var(--text); }
    .filter-btn.active { background: rgba(201,168,76,.15); border-color: var(--border-gold); color: var(--gold); }

    /* ---- UID ROW ---- */
    .uid-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .uid-row input {
      flex: 1; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 14px; color: var(--text); font-size: 14px;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif; outline: none;
      transition: border-color .2s;
    }
    .uid-row input:focus { border-color: var(--border-gold); }
    .uid-row input::placeholder { color: var(--text-3); }

    /* ---- BUTTON ---- */
    .btn {
      background: rgba(201,168,76,.15); border: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 8px 18px; color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif; transition: background .18s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: rgba(201,168,76,.28); }
    .btn-full { width: 100%; margin-top: 10px; padding: 12px; }

    /* ---- NOTICE ---- */
    .notice {
      background: rgba(201,168,76,.07); border: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 9px 14px; font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-2); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .notice a { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ---- CHAR GRID ---- */
    .char-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(120px, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .char-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 14px 10px;
      cursor: pointer; text-align: center; position: relative;
      transition: border-color .18s, background .18s, transform .15s;
    }
    .char-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); background: var(--card-hover); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .char-card.not-owned { opacity: 0.42; filter: grayscale(0.25); }
    .char-card.selected-char { border-color: var(--gold); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--gold); }
    .char-avatar {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); border: 2px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 24px; margin: 0 auto 8px;
    }
    .char-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.2; }
    .char-stars { font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .star5 { color: var(--geo); }
    .star4 { color: var(--electro); }
    .owned-tag {
      position: absolute; top: 6px; right: 6px; font-size: 9px;
      background: rgba(76,175,80,.2); color: var(--success);
      border: 1px solid rgba(76,175,80,.3); border-radius: 999px; padding: 1px 5px;
    }
    .char-role { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-3); margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ---- TOGGLE OWNED BUTTON ---- */
    .toggle-own-btn {
      width: 100%; margin-top: 7px; font-size: 10px; padding: 3px 6px;
      border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent; color: var(--text-3); cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif; transition: all .18s;
    }
    .toggle-own-btn:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); color: var(--gold-light); }

    /* ---- TEAM CARDS ---- */
    .team-card {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .team-card.can-use { border-color: rgba(76,175,80,.35); }
    .team-header {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .team-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
    .reaction-pill {
      font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 600;
      background: rgba(167,139,250,.15); color: #c4b5fd; border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,.2);
    }
    .diff-badge { font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 600; }
    .diff-easy { background: rgba(76,175,80,.15);  color: var(--success); }
    .diff-med  { background: rgba(255,152,0,.15); color: var(--warning); }
    .team-members { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 10px 0; }
    .member-chip {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .member-chip.missing { opacity: 0.48; }
    .team-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.65; }
    .team-status { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 8px; }
    .team-status.ok   { color: var(--success); }
    .team-status.warn { color: var(--warning); }

    /* ---- MAP ---- */
    .map-wrap {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .map-wrap svg { width: 100%; display: block; }
    .resource-dot { cursor: pointer; transition: r .15s, filter .15s; }
    .resource-dot:hover { filter: brightness(1.5); }
    .map-legend {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(165px, 1fr));
      gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .legend-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px; background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text);
      transition: border-color .18s;
    }
    .legend-item:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); }
    .legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .resource-popup {
      background: rgba(8,12,24,.96); border: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 16px; margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 13px; backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }
    .resource-popup a { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ---- BUILD ---- */
    .build-char-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(100px, 1fr));
      gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .build-char-btn {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 8px; cursor: pointer;
      text-align: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-2); font-family: 'Noto Sans Thai', sans-serif;
      transition: all .18s;
    }
    .build-char-btn:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); color: var(--text); }
    .build-char-btn.active { background: rgba(201,168,76,.12); border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
    .build-guide {
      background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 22px; display: none;
    }
    .build-section { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .build-label {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-3);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .06em; margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .build-value { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65; }
    .stat-pill {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-2); margin: 2px;
    }
    .tip-box {
      background: rgba(201,168,76,.07); border: 1px solid var(--border-gold);
      border-radius: 9px; padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.75; margin-top: 14px;
    }
    .tip-box strong { color: var(--gold); }
    .build-char-header {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .build-avatar {
      width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); border: 2px solid var(--border-gold);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28px;
    }
    .build-char-name {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    /* ---- EMPTY STATE ---- */
    .empty { text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; color: var(--text-3); font-size: 13px; }
    .empty-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 10px; }

    /* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .logo small { display: none; }
      .tab { padding: 8px 10px 10px; font-size: 12px; }
      .resin-num { font-size: 40px; }
      .char-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(100px, 1fr)); }
      .build-char-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(88px, 1fr)); }
      .card { padding: 14px 14px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="stars"></div>

<div class="app">
  <!-- ======== HEADER ======== -->
  <header>
    <div class="header-inner">
      <div class="logo">
        ✦ Genshin Companion
        <small>ตัวช่วยเล่น Genshin Impact ภาษาไทย</small>
      </div>
      <nav class="tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="เมนูหลัก">
        <button class="tab active" onclick="switchTab('daily',this)"   role="tab">📅 วันนี้</button>
        <button class="tab"        onclick="switchTab('chars',this)"   role="tab">👤 ตัวละคร</button>
        <button class="tab"        onclick="switchTab('teams',this)"   role="tab">⚔️ ทีม</button>
        <button class="tab"        onclick="switchTab('map',this)"     role="tab">🗺️ แผนที่</button>
        <button class="tab"        onclick="switchTab('build',this)"   role="tab">📖 บิลด์</button>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ======== MAIN ======== -->
  <main>

    <!-- ===== DAILY ===== -->
    <section class="section active" id="sec-daily">

      <!-- Resin Tracker -->
      <div class="card card-gold">
        <div class="card-title">💎 Original Resin Tracker</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <div class="resin-num" id="resin-num">160</div>
          <div style="font-size:16px;color:var(--text-3);padding-bottom:8px">/ 200</div>
          <div style="margin-left:auto;text-align:right;padding-bottom:6px">
            <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-3)">เต็มใน</div>
            <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--gold)" id="resin-time">เต็มแล้ว!</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="resin-bar-bg">
          <div class="resin-bar-fill" id="resin-fill" style="width:80%"></div>
        </div>
        <input type="range" min="0" max="200" value="160" id="resin-slider" oninput="updateResin(this.value)">
        <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:10px;color:var(--text-3);margin-top:4px">
          <span>0</span>
          <span style="color:var(--gold)">60 Resin = 1 Domain Run</span>
          <span>200 เต็ม</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Daily Tasks -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">☑️ งานประจำวัน
          <button class="btn" style="margin-left:auto;font-size:11px;padding:3px 10px" onclick="resetTasks()">รีเซ็ตทั้งหมด</button>
        </div>
        <div id="daily-tasks"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Today's Domains -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">🏯 โดเมนวันนี้ — <span class="accent" id="today-day-label"></span></div>
        <div id="today-domains"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Wish Pity Tracker -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">⭐ Wish Pity Tracker</div>
        <div id="wish-rows"></div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- ===== CHARACTERS ===== -->
    <section class="section" id="sec-chars">
      <div class="notice">
        💡 UID lookup ใช้ข้อมูลตัวอย่าง — เชื่อมต่อ
        <a href="https://enka.network/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Enka.Network API</a>
        จริงๆ เพื่อดึงข้อมูล showcase จาก UID ได้ | กด <strong style="color:var(--gold)">ติ๊ก/เลิกติ๊ก</strong> บนการ์ดเพื่ออัพเดทว่ามีตัวละครนั้นหรือยัง
      </div>

      <div class="uid-row">
        <input type="text" id="uid-input" placeholder="UID ของคุณ (เช่น 812345678)" maxlength="9" inputmode="numeric">
        <button class="btn" onclick="loadUID()">🔍 โหลด</button>
      </div>

      <div class="filter-row" id="el-filters">
        <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="setElFilter('all',this)">ทั้งหมด</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setElFilter('Pyro',this)"    style="color:var(--pyro)">🔥 Pyro</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setElFilter('Hydro',this)"   style="color:var(--hydro)">💧 Hydro</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" onclick="setElFilter('Anemo',this)"   style="color:var(--anemo)">🌀 Anemo</button>
